{"tid":716729,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥記三款「平包」今起加$1元","createTime":"2018-06-25T13:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:57:37.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"64712f06ea102edb723e857c389b6e66e819c4ea","tid":716729,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20130618/large/1371568661_d113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130618%2Flarge%2F1371568661_d113.jpg&h=f0c385f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被網民形容為「窮人救星」的麥當勞三款平價包，豬柳蛋漢堡、雙牛芝堡及麥香雞，今日11時起將會由8元，加價1元，變成9元一個。 <br />\n<br />\n麥當勞發言人解釋，加價是由於營運成本如租金及食材價格不斷上漲，又指今次只是調整了這三款漢堡價格，其他產品價格不變。 <br />\n<br />\n早前網上已有自稱是麥當勞的職員放風，預告三款平價包將加價1元，不少網民都指麥記搶錢，慨嘆以後「冇8蚊平包買」。 <br />\n<br />\n中文大學市場學系教授冼日明指，麥記今次挑選三款平價包加價，生活艱難的基層市民首當其衝。他又預計麥當勞其他售價較平的「超值選」產品很快會加價。"},{"pid":"5ae939d0c4ec7c0a100e053488b30eac097ca017","tid":716729,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"金拱門點加法 同加煙價一樣 <br />\nd人一樣照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6550778c9bfd18e8582519d117eb51adf09806a6","tid":716729,"uid":147264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"我都想去番9蚊嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3884f66399f28f6f928c4e3eddbb953bae24463","tid":716729,"uid":151664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"雙牛芝堡好正 又抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5153c2503c65649178ffd7f0a94cedda4ef9a31","tid":716729,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"當年啲人話加到十蚊就罷食，依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?